# Portfolio Design System

Every **new** section must match Hero and Case Studies. Do **not** redesign Hero, Case Studies, or other existing sections unless explicitly asked.

## Reference implementations

- **Hero:** `src/sections/Hero/Hero.module.css` â€” composition card, nav, typography, fade-up
- **Case Studies:** `src/sections/Projects/CaseStudyRow.module.css` â€” card grid, chips, actions, spacing
- **Tokens:** `src/styles/tokens/` â€” colors, spacing, typography, motion, layout

## Principles

Premium SaaS landing page feel: clean, readable, professional, minimal noise. One cohesive productâ€”not independent blocks.

## Color

- Use only the existing blue palette (`--color-primary`, `--color-primary-soft`, `--color-accent-soft`)
- Warm neutrals for bg/surface/text (`--color-bg`, `--color-surface`, `--color-text`, `--color-text-muted`)
- **No** new accent colors (no purple, green, orange, or random gradients)
- Soft blue tints only via `color-mix` or `--color-primary-soft` on surfaces

## Cards

Match Case Study / Hero composition:

```css
background-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-surface) 94%, var(--color-primary-soft));
border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
padding: var(--space-5); /* var(--space-6) on lg */
```

Hover: `border-color: var(--color-border-strong); box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);`

Chips: reuse Case Study `.techChip` pattern (surface bg, border, `--radius-sm`, `--text-xs`).

## Typography

- Heading font: `var(--font-heading)` (Sora), body: `var(--font-body)` (Inter)
- Section titles via `SectionHeader`; card titles use `--weight-semibold`, `--leading-snug`, `--tracking-tight`
- Do not invent new heading sizes or stylesâ€”mirror Hero / Case Studies hierarchy

## Spacing

- Section shell: `Section` + `Container` + `SectionHeader`
- Section padding: `--section-padding-y` / `--section-padding-y-mobile`
- Inter-section rhythm: `--space-5`â€“`--space-6` header margins; use `--space-*` scale only
- Avoid large empty gaps; keep vertical rhythm consistent with Projects / Research

## Animation

Subtle only; respect `prefers-reduced-motion`:

- Fade up: `opacity 0 â†’ 1`, `translateY(0.5rem â†’ 0)`, `--duration-slow`, `--ease-out`
- Soft hover on cards/chips/buttons
- No dramatic motion, bounce, or flashy effects

## Layout & responsive

- Desktop / tablet / mobile must stay visually balanced
- Two-column layouts collapse cleanly (stack content â†’ visual)
- Reuse existing breakpoints: 640px, 768px, 1024px

## Components

- Buttons: `src/components/ui/Button` with icon + label (see Case Study actions)
- Content: colocate copy in `src/content/`
- CSS Modules per section; no inline styles or one-off color hex values

## Checklist (new section)

- [ ] Uses design tokens only
- [ ] Card matches glass-adjacent surface + border + shadow pattern
- [ ] Typography matches Hero / Case Studies
- [ ] Spacing uses `--space-*` and shared section layout
- [ ] Subtle fade-up entrance; hover elevation on cards
- [ ] Responsive at 640 / 768 / 1024
- [ ] No new accent colors or flashy animation
